  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Analyzing Brand Fundamentals**\n\nI\'m currently immersed in understanding the Deyar brand. The focus is on translating their elegant, playful ethos and storytelling roots into a modern, responsive website. I\'m focusing on the uploaded logo and brand PDF to extract key guidelines. The aim is to create a design that visually represents the cafe\'s core values.\n\n\n**Visualizing Core Aesthetics**\n\nI\'m now deeply visualizing the brand\'s aesthetic. I\'m focusing on the Himachali landscape, the symbolic Himalayan bear, and the deodar forests. I\'m prioritizing editorial elegance, cozy warmth, and an artisanal feel. The color palette of warm rust, cocoa, dark coffee, and creamy off-white is central, with imagery like the bear with a pinecone. I aim for elegant typography and clean layouts with textures like coffee beans.\n\n\n**Defining Functional Scope**\n\nI\'ve clarified the project scope. Building a React SPA with interactive reservations and online ordering seems correct. I\'m focusing on client-side simulation for these features, including cart, checkout, and delivery mockups, given the lack of specified real API integration. The priority is to meet the precise user request, avoiding any unnecessary features like AI recommendations or backend components.\n\n\n**Refining Feature Implementation**\n\nI\'m now prioritizing the exact feature set. My focus is on delivering the precise scope requested, and building the Homepage, Menu, About Us, and Contact pages, including the specified functionalities: online ordering system (with cart drawer and mock delivery), a fully functional reservation system with a date/time picker, and Google Maps integration or custom-styled map components. I\'m ensuring everything works locally.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I\'ll start by checking the existing files in the repository to see how the project is structured. I will read `metadata.json`, `package.json`, and `src/App.tsx` first."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 4
      nanos: 592086867
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
