    modified_response: "I will create our updated `/src/index.css` file with custom Google Fonts and custom color palette variables inside the Tailwind v4 `@theme` block. This sets up \"Deyar\" colors like Rich Cream, Rust Ochre, Cocoa Brown, Pine, and Espresso, plus typography pairing for our elegant layout."
