  planner_response {
    modified_response: "I have updated and verified the cafe web application to fully incorporate the **Clean Minimalism** design theme across all remaining pages and interactive modules. \n\nThe aesthetic changes ensure a harmonious, flat and sharp look-and-feel that relies on elegant white-space density and natural earth tones instead of busy, heavily rounded components.\n\n### Details of the Completed Work:\n\n* **Contact Section Updates**: Adjusted all form input fields, textareas, and submit buttons to use sharp-corner styles (`rounded-sm`). Simplified card container borders and set secondary badge highlights to use cleaner, flat borders mimicking premium architectural guidelines.\n* **Forest Cartography Map**: Redesigned the coordinates radar indicators into crisp, concentric square locator pings and styled the altitude parameters and surrounding map wrapper to fit a precise, flat visual aesthetic.\n* **Interactive Cart Side Drawer**: Styled the entire order bag, customized food-item containers, counter controllers, custom note boxes, and third-party delivery links (Swiggy / Zomato) to match the minimalist theme perfectly.\n* **Aesthetic Footer Integrations**: Styled the email newsletter input box, subscription confirmation states, and the Bear seal logo to feature sharp frame outlines (`rounded-sm`) instead of high-ellipse corners.\n* **System Integrity & Deployment**: Verified all code syntax and TypeScript definitions using internal compiler tests, ensuring that the full application builds cleanly."
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
