    modified_response: "I have successfully streamlined the **Deyar Cafe** application into a polished, high-performance Minimum Viable Product (MVP) tailored specifically to your latest specifications:\n\n### \360\237\214\237 MVP Key Deliverables\n\n*   **Clean Minimalism Theme**: Fully maintained the beautiful, earthy, high-contrast visual theme featuring warm tones and modern typography pairing **Inter** with **Libre Baskerville**.\n*   **Roasted Coffee Beans Hero Background**: Integrated a beautiful, subtle background texture of roasted coffee beans in the main Hero section, rendering at an eye-pleasing low opacity to provide depth while keeping display text perfectly readable.\n*   **Direct Hero Navigation Links**: Implemented convenient, high-contrast quick links for **Menu**, **About Us**, and **Contact** directly below the main Hero section\'s action buttons, giving visitors instant pathways across the site.\n*   **Simplified Showcase Menu**:\n    *   Removed the complex, in-app shopping cart engine, overlay drawer, product price modifiers, and add-to-cart controls as requested.\n    *   Each menu item now displays beautiful imagery, custom botanical tags, detailed descriptions, and transparent item pricing cleanly.\n    *   Clicking **\"Explore Details\"** opens an elegant, non-interactive informational modal showing available recipe sizing, options, and barista remarks.\n    *   Integrated a **Zomato delivery gateway banner** to let customers order from regional carriers directly.\n*   **Removed Table Bookings & Reservations**: Completely removed the reservation calendars, booking buttons, sidebar icons, and scheduling forms from both the Main Navigation, Footer, Hero, and Page layouts. Removed all dead files from the project structure to maintain a production-ready codebase."
